229
00:16:08,701 --> 00:16:12,364
<i>I should, uh, call my family</i>
<i>with the news.</i>

230
00:16:17,076 --> 00:16:19,670
I followed through
on your paperwork.

231
00:16:19,746 --> 00:16:22,544
