Why are you doing this?

258
00:18:05,919 --> 00:18:10,652
The medical profession.
It's about the relief of suffering.

259
00:18:10,723 --> 00:18:13,214
Remember?

260
00:18:13,293 --> 00:18:15,386
[Phone Beeps]

261
00:18:39,619 --> 00:18:41,849
[Whistling]

