00:19:56,796 --> 00:19:58,730
<i>[Man]</i>
<i>Let's go.! Let's move.! Right in here.!</i>

280
00:19:58,798 --> 00:20:00,766
- <i>[Woman] What do you got?</i>
- [Chattering]

281
00:20:19,419 --> 00:20:21,683
<i>[Woman On P.A.]</i>
<i>Dr. Fletcher to Administration, please.</i>

