00:22:24,377 --> 00:22:26,743
<i>Attended Millbrook Elementary.</i>

302
00:22:27,813 --> 00:22:29,747
Photographic memory.

303
00:22:30,983 --> 00:22:33,918
And I'm sure I have
enough in here right now...

