<i>in my power to bring you back.</i>

423
00:31:51,729 --> 00:31:54,323
You shouldn't be lying here.

424
00:31:56,334 --> 00:31:58,495
You didn't deserve this.

425
00:32:32,436 --> 00:32:36,395
SL-27?

426
00:32:41,145 --> 00:32:45,946
